{"type":"message","id":"593a5b3e","parentId":"4ab45fb9","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:22:04.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，搜索已停止。现在让我给用户一些更实用的解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，针对sign in无效的问题，我给你几个更直接的解决方案：\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案1：完全卸载后重装（最推荐）\n1. 打开\"设置\" → \"应用\" → \"已安装的应用\"\n2. 找到Tailscale，点击卸载\n3. 重启电脑\n4. 重新下载官网安装包安装：https://tailscale.com/download/windows\n5. 安装后立即以管理员身份运行\n\n### 方案2：检查是否有安全软件拦截\n- 暂时关闭Windows Defender实时保护（测试用）\n- 如果有其他杀毒软件（360、火绒等），暂时禁用\n- 再尝试sign in\n\n### 方案3：重置网络\n以管理员身份打开PowerShell，运行：\n```powershell\nnetsh winsock reset\nnetsh int ip reset\nipconfig /release\nipconfig /renew\n```\n然后重启电脑\n\n### 方案4：手动触发登录\n让我尝试找到Tailscale并通过命令行启动登录："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_017kc8cq0d9xuaz0xb40d2e7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Command tailscale -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; $env:PATH -split ';' | Where-Object { $_ -like \"*tailscale*\" }","workdir":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":16162,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16515,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772590914805}}
