{"type":"message","id":"3f0cc32a","parentId":"c4195c18","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:22:24.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来Tailscale的可执行文件位置不太好找。让我给用户提供最实用的建议，先让他们尝试完全卸载重装。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，综合来看，我建议你先尝试**方案1（完全卸载重装）**，这通常能解决这类问题。\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 右键点击系统托盘的Tailscale图标 → 退出\n2. 打开设置 → 应用 → 已安装的应用 → 找到Tailscale → 卸载\n3. 重启电脑\n4. 重新下载安装：https://tailscale.com/download/windows\n5. **重要**：安装完成后，右键点击Tailscale → 以管理员身份运行\n6. 再尝试sign in\n\n如果重装后还是不行，我们再试试其他方案。你先试试看？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":10197,"output":198,"cacheRead":6456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772590938793}}
